4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT REVISING TAX INCREMENT FINANCING LAWS RELATED TO
5 THE LEVIES INCLUDED IN THE CALCULATION OF THE TAX INCREMENT; PROVIDING THAT CERTAIN
6 SCHOOL LEVIES AND DEBT SERVICE LEVIES ARE EXCLUDED WHEN CALCULATING THE TAX
7 INCREMENT FOR NEWLY CREATED DISTRICTS; AMENDING SECTION 7-15-4286, MCA; AND
8 PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE EFFECTIVE DATE AND AN APPLICABILITY DATE.”
9
